{"tid":2077392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"微軟宣佈計劃將美國管理層黑人數量增加一倍 為反種族歧視作出貢獻 解決工作環境中種族不平等問題","createTime":"2020-06-24T08:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T09:30:16.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"88a1f43e46e22b443de5ae9b9a119d9e2124f727","tid":2077392,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:55:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2678557/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96%E3%80%91%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E6%93%AC%E5%B0%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%A4%E9%BB%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E9%87%8F%E7%BF%BB%E5%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2678557%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258F%258D%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E6%2597%258F%25E6%25AD%25A7%25E8%25A6%2596%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BB%259F%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E9%25BB%2591%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8%25E9%2587%258F%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E5%2580%258D&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=7a1d097f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2678557/%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96%E3%80%91%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E6%93%AC%E5%B0%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%A4%E9%BB%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E9%87%8F%E7%BF%BB%E5%80%8D</a><br />\n「黑人的命很重要」（Black Lives Matter, BLM）運動在全美持續，科技大廠也紛紛發生支持並付諸實踐，微軟（Microsoft）本周二（23日）制定了一個5年多元化目標，力求解決工作環境中種族不平等問題，作為對美國反種族歧視示威活動的響應。<br />\n<br />\n微軟表示，將追加投資1.5億美元，用於提高企業的多元化和包容性，到2025年將其美國業務中的黑人和非裔美國經理、高級個人貢獻者（senior individual contributor）和高級領導人（senior leaders）數量增加一倍。<br />\n<br />\n相關文章：反種族歧視浪潮 黑人牙膏將改名爲__ 牙膏？<br />\n<br />\n本月較早時，Google也宣布，Google表示，公司將努力增加擔任高階職位的黑人員工數量，到2025年至少30％的領導職位將由少數族裔員工擔任。"},{"pid":"05febcb5eb2a1ca650404b72dd2b14dcc2e4b5ff","tid":2077392,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https